CommentBody:
We recreated a fresh File System Overview job and copied the analysis task and newly created report from the preexisting job to the new job.

Additionally, we discovered that the issue on ticket 00414694 involving the Temp DB storage capacity issue is related to the creation of the Share Details summary report not properly generating. We also discovered that the host list summary report isn't generated due to an SQL server connection issue. These reported issues may be alleviated by rebooting the SQL server after making changes to the SQL host Pagefile and switching from the capped 12GB to system managed on the C:.
